{"tid":1017959,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVBuddy都有　連詩雅揸實新城獎影相","createTime":"2019-02-12T00:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T08:48:20.000Z","uid":81228,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"400546bb79c1e34c84d8090795589220846e4bab","tid":1017959,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T00:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/2/1549810282_os-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F2%2F1549810282_os-1280w.jpg&h=e151d13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/2/1549810293_wM-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F2%2F1549810293_wM-1280w.png&h=1f9ee67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/2/1549810288_5h-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F2%2F1549810288_5h-1280w.png&h=6efc98dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/2/1549810285_cX-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F2%2F1549810285_cX-1280w.jpg&h=066a47a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前DJ Colin指北角渣華道天橋底發現有一個2013年的「新城勁爆躍進歌手」獎座，在一堆舊鞋當中。當年拿得此獎的有羅力威、連詩雅、龍小菌、蔚雨芯及吳彤，事後他們都不停指自己並非「兇手」，龍小菌及已移居加國的吳彤就po相證自己清白，連詩雅亦都托人在公司的獎櫃拍照已證清白。剩下蔚雨芯及羅力威未有提供照片，前者稱公司搬office，獎座暫時在迷你倉內，而羅力威稱自己家住九龍，獎項不會在港島出現。<br />\n<br />\n雖然連詩雅有托人影獎座，但基於「有圖都未必有真相」，不少網民質疑是舊有照片。連詩雅今日再與獎座影合照，更見到她身後的獎櫃有不少獎座，就連TVBuddy也在獎櫃上。她的同事更在照片上留言謂︰「2013獎項一直都在，閒人請你癈話少講。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/tv-bubby%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89-%E9%80%A3%E8%A9%A9%E9%9B%85%E6%8F%B8%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E7%8D%8E%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8-160893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2Ft